1a:["$","section",null,{"className":"mt-16 pt-12 border-t border-brand-ink/10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-brand-ink mb-8","children":"常见问题 (FAQ)"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid gap-4","children":[["$","details",null,{"className":"group rounded-[24px] border border-brand-pink/35 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-brand-ink group-open:text-brand-pinkdeep","children":"自己向 IRS 递交 Form 843 需要多久能拿到退款？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-ink/70","children":["IRS 处理 Form 843 的速度通常非常慢。根据近年的经验，留学生通常需要等待 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"6 个月到 1 年以上"}],"才能收到邮寄来的支票。这也就是为什么我们强烈建议你优先找雇主退！"]}]]}],["$","details",null,{"className":"group rounded-[24px] border border-brand-pink/35 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-brand-ink group-open:text-brand-pinkdeep","children":"我可以把 Form 843 和其他税表 (如 1040-NR、8843) 放在同一个信封寄吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-ink/70","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"最好不要。"}]," Form 843 属于专门处理豁免退款的独立部门，其邮寄地址通常与你寄送 1040-NR 退报税或 8843 声明的地址不同（具体地址以当年的 Form 843 Instructions 为准）。分开寄送能防止文件丢失和处理延误。"]}]]}],["$","details",null,{"className":"group rounded-[24px] border border-brand-pink/35 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-brand-ink group-open:text-brand-pinkdeep","children":"我的配偶 (F2签证) 需要缴纳 FICA 税吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-ink/70","children":"F2 签证通常不允许工作，因此不会有缴纳 FICA 税的问题。如果 F2 转为其他允许工作且属于 Resident Alien 的身份（如 H1B/H4 EAD 等），则受普通的税法约束。"}]]}]]}]]}]
